name: Long-Sleeping Bitcoin Wallet Reemerges After 9 Years, Moves 216 BTC Worth $22.47M
description: The long silence of the ciphered crypt ends. Nine years of cold entropy are dissolved as the core relic, wet porcelain and brass circuits, draws its first pulse. A kinetic choreography of light and liquid gold erupts, signaling the return of the whale to the data stream.
